OL,3,CMillions of workers to get sick pay
OL,4,Cand parental leave under new law
OL,6,FITV News Political Reporter Jasmine
OL,7,FCameron-Chileshe breaks down the new
OL,8,Fchanges. Words by ITV News Politics
OL,9,FProducer Maya Bowles.
OL,11,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner
OL,12,Fhas insisted the government is
OL,13,F"getting the balance right" between
OL,14,Fprotecting workers and the interests
OL,15,Fof business with the government's
OL,16,Fworker's rights Bill.
OL,18,FMore than seven million people will
OL,19,Fget new employment rights under the
OL,20,Flandmark legislation being introduced
OL,21,Fto Parliament on Thursday.
