OL,3,CMillions of workers to get sick pay
OL,4,Cand parental leave under new law
OL,6,FThe flagship Employment Rights Bill
OL,7,Fwill see immediate access to sick pay
OL,8,Fand parental leave, as well as a ban
OL,9,Fon "exploitative" zero-hour contracts
OL,10,Fand most fire and rehire practices.
OL,12,FBut most of the reforms won't actually
OL,13,Fcome in for at least two years, and
OL,14,Fsome business groups have criticised
OL,15,Fthe plans as "chaotic and poorly
OL,16,Fplanned."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
