OL,4,Cand parental leave under new law
OL,6,FSpeaking on a visit to a logistics
OL,7,Fcompany in Durham, Rayner insisted the
OL,8,Fpackage was "pro-business and pro-
OL,9,Fworker", and said "some things will
OL,10,Ftake a little bit longer, because
OL,11,Fthese are the biggest upgrades in
OL,12,Fworker's rights in a generation."
OL,14,FThe new plans will give workers the
OL,15,Fright to claim unfair dismissal from
OL,16,Fday one in the job, rather than two
OL,17,Fyears - but there will also be a
OL,18,Fprobation period to allow businesses
OL,19,Fto dismiss people "fairly" if they
OL,20,Faren't doing well at the job.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
