OL,4,Cand parental leave under new law
OL,6,FThere are still a number of areas
OL,7,Fwhere tension remains, particularly
OL,8,Faround the definition of
OL,9,F"exploitative" zero-hour contracts,
OL,10,Fand the length of the probation period
OL,11,Ffor "fair" dismissal.
OL,13,FThere will be consultations on the new
OL,14,Fstatutory period, with ministers
OL,15,Fpromising employers - the government
OL,16,Fsay they would like the period to be
OL,17,Fnine months, to the frustration of
OL,18,Fsome unions who would like it to be
OL,19,Fshorter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
