OL,4,Cand parental leave under new law
OL,6,FThe government say they will hold
OL,7,Fconsultations on many of the measures,
OL,8,Fwhich is why most of the reforms won't
OL,9,Fcome in until 2026. Some secondary
OL,10,Flegislation will also need to be
OL,11,Fintroduced as the Bill progresses.
OL,13,FSome measures, such as the right to
OL,14,F"switch off" at the end of a working
OL,15,Fday, are not in the Bill but will be
OL,16,Fincluded in a so-called "Next Steps"
OL,17,Fdocument for further consideration and
OL,18,Fconsultation.
