OL,3,CMillions of workers to get sick pay
OL,4,Cand parental leave under new law
OL,6,FThe Bill also spells out day one
OL,7,Frights for paternity, parental and
OL,8,Fbereavement leave for millions of
OL,9,Fworkers, while statutory sick pay will
OL,10,Fbe paid from the first day of a worker
OL,11,Fbeing sick rather than having to wait
OL,12,Funtil the fourth day.
OL,14,FAround 30,000 fathers or partners will
OL,15,Fbe eligible for paternity leave, while
OL,16,Fan extra 1.5 million parents will have
OL,17,Fthe right to unpaid leave from day one.
OL,19,FThe Bill doesn't however make any
OL,20,Fchanges to statutory maternity or
OL,21,Fpaternity pay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
