OL,6,FWorkers on those contracts will now be
OL,7,Fentitled to a "reasonable" number of
OL,8,Fshifts and financial compensation if a
OL,9,Fshift is cancelled or cut short.
OL,11,FTUC General Secretary Paul Nowak said
OL,12,Fthe Bill "signals a seismic shift away
OL,13,Ffrom the Tories' low pay, low rights,
OL,14,Flow productivity economy", but "there
OL,15,Fis still detail to be worked through."
